  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reading Centre in Congo (DRC)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will build a reading center in eastern Congo to teach basic reading and writing skills to children, mostly orphans who have been left behind after 15 years of civil war that killed over 5 million people.  3.5 million children in Congo are not attending elementary school.  IWOF will build a reading center on land owned by Grace Orphanage. Many widows in the area cannot read, and classes will be offered to these women who care for children, some not even their own.</narrative>
  </description>
